igo]]<ref>Greg A. Vaughan. ''Mythic Monsters Revisited'' ([[Paizo Publishing]], 2012)</ref> || Pathfinder Campaign Setting ||2012\n|-\n| ''Inner Sea Bestiary'' - Apostasy Wraith, Charnel Colossus, Petrified Maiden, Shadow Giant, Thin Man, Whirlmaw<ref>[[James Jacobs (game designer)|James Jacobs]], et al. ''Inner Sea Bestiary'' ([[Paizo Publishing]], 2012)</ref> || Pathfinder Campaign Setting || 2012\n|-\n| ''Cradle of Night'' (with [[James Jacobs (game designer)|James Jacobs]], Neil Spicer, and [[F. Wesley Schneider]])<ref>[[James Jacobs (game designer)|James Jacobs]], Neil Spicer, [[F. Wesley Schneider]], and Greg A. Vaughan. ''Cradle of Night'' ([[Paizo Publishing]], 2018)</ref> || Pathfinder Module || 2018\n|}\n\n===== [[Pathfinder (periodicals)|Pathfinder]] Society Scenarios =====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Number !! Title !! Season !! Year\n|-\n| PSS 03 || ''Murder on the Silken Caravan''<ref>Greg A. Vaughan. ''PSS 03: Murder on the Silken Caravan'' ([[Paizo Publishing]], 2008)</ref> || 0 || 2008\n|-\n| PSS 20 || ''King Xeros of Old Azlant''<ref>Greg A. Vaughan. ''PSS 20: King Xeros of Old Azlant'' ([[Paizo Publishing]], 2009)</ref> || 0 || 2009\n|-\n| PSS 42 || ''Echoes of the Everwar, Part II: Watcher of the Ages''<ref>Greg A. Vaughan. ''PSS 42: Echoes of the Everwar, Part II: Watcher of the Ages'' ([[Paizo Publishing]], 2010)</ref> || 1 || 2010\n|-\n| PSS 02-06 || ''The Heresy of Man, Part I: First Heresy'' (with Kevin Wright)<ref>Kevin Wright and Greg A. Vaughan. ''PSS 02-06: The Heresy of Man, Part I: First Heresy'' ([[Paizo Publishing]], 2010)</ref> || 2 || 2010\n|-\n| PSS 02-07 || ''The Heresy of Man, Part II: Where Dark Things Sleep'' (with Kevin Wright)<ref>Kevin Wright and Greg A. Vaughan. ''PSS 02-07: The Heresy of Man, Part II: Where Dark Things Sleep'' ([[Paizo Publishing]], 2010)</ref> || 2 || 2010\n|-\n| PSS 02-09 || ''The Heresy of Man, Part III: Beneath Forgotten Sands'' (with Kevin Wright)<ref>Kevin Wright and Greg A. Vaughan. ''PSS 02-09: