 Place in the World\"\n| Shamarr Allen & The Underdawgs\n|''True Orleans''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Double Dribble\"\n| MC Shakie\n|''The Return''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Erky Derky\"\n| Jay Driggy\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''Beats for the Streetz''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"A Commercial Break\"\n| Jay Driggy, Hasizzle\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Livin' It Up\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2019\n|Dappa\n|''The Paper Chase''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Shake It\"\n|[[Charli XCX]], [[Cupcakke]], [[Brooke Candy]], [[Pabllo Vittar]]\n|''[[Charli (album)|Charli]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Good Time\"\n|[[The Soul Rebels]], [[Denisia]], Passport P\n|''Poetry in Motion''\n|}\n\n====Music videos====\n*2010: \"Na Who Mad\" \u2013 <small>music video released 2011</small>\n*2010: \"Y'all Get Back Now\" \u2013 <small>music video released 2011</small>\n*2010: \"Excuse\" \u2013 <small>music video released 2011</small>\n*2014: \"Explode\" \u2013 <small>music video released 2014</small>\n*2014: \"Mo Azz\" \u2013 <small>music video released 2014</small>\n*2016: \"Crazy\" \u2013 <small>music video released 2016</small>\n*2016: \"Make It Jingle\" \u2013 <small>music video released 2016</small>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist| refs =<ref name=\"ya\">[{{BillboardURLbyName|artist=galactic|chart=all}} Galactica Position on Billboard]</ref><ref name=\"sullivan2011\">Sullivan, Michael (January 20, 2011). [http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118030583/ GLAAD names media noms.] ''[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]''</ref><ref name=\"zeichner2011\">Zeichner, Naomi (March 23, 2011). [http://www.thefader.com/2011/03/23/video-big-freedia-yall-get-back-now/ Video: Big Freedia, \"Y'all Get Back Now.] ''[[The FADER]]''</ref><ref name=\"dodero2010\">Dodero, Camille (May 25, 2010). [http://blogs.villagevoice.com/music/2010/05/hillstock_takes.php Hoodstock Takes Bed-Stuy with Big Freedia and Ninjasonik, Leaves People Bruised Like Crack Whores.] ''[[Village Voice]]''</ref><ref name=\"fensterstock\">Fensterstock, Allison (October 7, 2010). [http: